TEXT.TITLE: RECENT PROPOSED OFFERINGS FILED WITH SEC
TEXT.BODY: The following are proposed securities offerings filed recently with the Securities and Exchange Commission: Outboard Marine Corp - Up to 200 mln dlrs of debt securities on terms to be set at the time of sale through an underwriting group that is expected to include Salomon Brothers Inc and Morgan Stanley and Co Inc. Osborn Communications Corp - Initial offering of one mln shares of common stock and 30 mln dlrs of senior subordinated ten-year notes through a group led by E.F. Hutton and Co Inc. Reuter
